    report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    report_date DATE,
    report_type VARCHAR,
    shareholder_id UUID,
    regulatory_body_id UUID
);

CREATE TABLE financial_reports (
 report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 report_date DATE,
 company_name VARCHAR(255),
 total_assets DECIMAL,
 total_liabilities DECIMAL,
 total_equity DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE shareholders (
 shareholder_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 shareholder_name VARCHAR(255),
 email_address VARCHAR(255),
 shares_owned INT,

);

CREATE TABLE FinancialReports (
 report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 report_name TEXT,
 report_date DATE,
 report_type TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Shareholders (
 shareholder_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 shareholder_name TEXT,
 shareholder_email TEXT,
 shareholder_address TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE RegulatoryBodies (
 body_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 body_name TEXT,
 body_type TEXT,
 body_address TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ReportHistory (
 history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 report_id INT,
 shareholder_id INT,
 body_id INT,
 submission_date DATE,
 status TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE financial_reports (
 report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 report_date DATE NOT NULL,
 report_type VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 total_assets DECIMAL,
 total_liabilities DECIMAL,
 total_equity DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE shareholders (
 shareholder_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 shareholder_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 shareholder_email VARCHAR(255),
 shareholder_address VARCHAR(255),
 shares_owned INT
);

CREATE TABLE regulatory_bodies (
 body_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 body_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 body_type VARCHAR(255),
 contact_person VARCHAR(255),
 contact_email VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE company_assets (
 asset_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 asset_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 asset_type VARCHAR(255),
 purchase_date DATE,
 purchase_amount DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE company_liabilities (
 liability_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 liability_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 liability_type VARCHAR(255),
 due_date DATE,
 amount_owed DECIMAL
);
